				<div class="paragraph-aux">
					<p class="section_paragraph-full">The project is focused on simplify the ticket purchasing and the overall clients experience on public transports, creating new tools and improving the usability of the existing vending machines. Based on our research we discovered strange behaviours of people for buying  </p>
