				<header class="paragraph_caption">QUICK PURCHASE SHORTCUT </header>
				<p class="section_paragraph-full">Buying a ticket on a kiosk requires an average time of 4 seconds, instead 30s on the vending machine. The shortcut allows to buy the most used ticket in the same amount of time on a smartphone.</p>
				<br></br>
				<header class="paragraph_caption">CONTRACT RECHARGE </header>
				<p class="section_paragraph-full">Recharging the travel card is always a big issue. This app send a warning before the contract expiration and the user can track the state of validity.</p>
				<br></br>
				<header class="paragraph_caption">BUY N' SEND </header>
				<p class="section_paragraph-full">Trough the "wallet" function it's possible to buy tickets in advantage manage the purchased and send them to your friends.</p>
				<br></br>
				<header class="paragraph_caption">GET IT FROM SEARCH </header>
				<p class="section_paragraph-full">Get tickets faster while searching places on map tools. Designed specifically for tourists and foreign people.</p>
